&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write and optimize T-SQL queries, stored procedures, and views against MS SQL Server&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain Java-based add-on products that extend Infinite Campus functionality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write custom reports using SQL Server Reporting Services (SSRS) based on district requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with senior developers to translate client requests into technical specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test, debug, and document your work so it’s ready to hand off to clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other job-related duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;

